<h2>{{site_name}}</h2>
<p>
    <strong>{{site_name}}</strong> is powered by
    <a href="https://github.com/Xalior/byob-oidc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BYOB-OIDC</a>,
    an open-source, plugin-based OpenID Connect identity provider.
</p>
<p>
    BYOB-OIDC provides secure authentication, authorization, and single identity federation
    through a modular plugin architecture. Every major subsystem &mdash; user storage, session
    management, multi-factor authentication, and UI theming &mdash; is a swappable plugin.
</p>

<h4>Features</h4>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Standards-Compliant:</strong> Full OpenID Connect provider built on <code>oidc-provider</code>.</li>
    <li><strong>Plugin Architecture:</strong> Swap providers, sessions, MFA, themes, and extensions without changing core code.</li>
    <li><strong>Privacy by Design:</strong> Self-hosted, no third-party dependencies for core identity flows.</li>
    <li><strong>Federation-Ready:</strong> Issue and verify tokens for service-to-service interoperability.</li>
</ul>

